survey_response.review_text: ****** **** *** *** **** *** *** ******* ** ****** ***********. I was initially scared of dental procedures but Dr. Mark made my treatment a pleasant experience... Now I blindly trust his diagnosis and treatment plan cause he is so accurate.. His personal care for each of his patients and follow ups are impeccable... I will definitely recommend Dr.Mark without second thoughts.. Also treatments were of good quality and affordable... Thank you Dr.Mark & his team...

Dr Mark is really good. He explains everything very clearly and makes the procedure extremely easy. I would surely recommend him to anyone. My mother always goes to Dr Mark. She is 75 and loves the dentist experience because of Dr Mark.
Great doc and support staff. Highly recommenced. Went for a follow up and consult for future dental plans and procedures.

Dr. Mark was the second lead doctor on my cosmetic treatment, the team gave me such an amazing smile that I had the confidence and look I needed to win the Femina Miss India title 2012 (just a month after treatment). Since then Dr. Mark has been treating me for the past 8 years. He is extremely patient and kind, answering all queries and explaining all procedures in detail before starting any procedure. He is committed to 'no pain' treatments and even though I used to hate going to the dentist growing up, now a visit to Mark's clinic is a peaceful experience with no expectation of pain or trauma. Dr. Mark also has a great eye for cosmetic adjustments that need to be made, he knows exactly how to enhance your smile while still keeping a natural look. He uses only the latest technology and best products and his pricing is very fair. Overall would recommend Dr. Mark 100%

Dr Mark is amazing ..not just as a doctor but as a person. Very gentle and caring. Very knowledgeable too. 
I had a simple problem.. but somehow got complicated because of my earlier sinusitis. He took the trouble of calling my son and going with us to my ENT doc to check on what my problem could be. 
He is truly wonderful. Thank you Doc.

Dentist appointments are something a person looks forward to . At least that has been my experience so far . With Mark’s cheerful attitude and chatting away things gets done in no time . That’s exactly how I felt . The 20 minutes flew and he was done and I was comfortable and relaxed .

Dr. Thomas was fantastic - he explained the issues, laid out treatment options, planned a treatment route, and answered every single question I came up with. He managed to finally fix long-standing issues many dentists in the past hadn't been able to, and I would recommend him to anyone who is looking for a responsive and very talented doctor for dental work.
